{"id":11887,"date":"2024-03-20T15:05:16","date_gmt":"2024-03-20T09:35:16","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/?p=11887"},"modified":"2024-03-28T13:06:42","modified_gmt":"2024-03-28T07:36:42","slug":"add-new-products","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/add-new-products\/","title":{"rendered":"Add New Products"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<iframe title=\"how to manage your product\" width=\"750\" height=\"422\" src=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/3whIfILyDl0?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen><\/iframe>\n<\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#cd3636\" class=\"has-inline-color\">How to add Products In list<\/mark><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"739\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/Screenshot_20240321-135400-1-739x1024.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-11960\" style=\"width:439px;height:auto\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/Screenshot_20240321-135400-1-739x1024.png 739w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/Screenshot_20240321-135400-1-462x640.png 462w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/Screenshot_20240321-135400-1-768x1064.png 768w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/Screenshot_20240321-135400-1.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 739px) 100vw, 739px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<ol>\n<li><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#cd3636\" class=\"has-inline-color\">Upload Photo:<\/mark>  \u0906\u092a\u0915\u0947 \u0926\u094d\u0935\u093e\u0930\u093e \u0932\u093f\u090f \u0917\u092f\u0947 \u0915\u094b\u0908 \u092d\u0940 New Product \u0915\u094b Upload Photo \u0915\u0947 \u0938\u0939\u092f\u0924\u093e \u0938\u0947 \u0906\u092a \u0905\u092a\u0928\u0947 list \u092e\u0947\u0902 \u0938\u092e\u093f\u0932 \u0915\u0930 \u0938\u0915\u0924\u0947 \u0939\u0948\u0964<br><br>2. \u091c\u092c \u0906\u092a \u0905\u092a\u0928\u0947 Product \u0915\u094b Select \u0915\u0930 \u0932\u0947\u0924\u0947 \u0939\u0948 \u0924\u094b\u0964 \u0906\u092a\u0915\u0947 \u0938\u093e\u092e\u0928\u0947 \u0909\u0938 products \u0915\u0947 \u0938\u093e\u0930\u0947 details \u0915\u094b Fill-up \u0915\u0930\u0928\u0947 \u0915\u0947 \u0932\u093f\u090f  Panel \u0926\u093f\u092f\u0947 \u0917\u092f\u0947 \u0939\u0948\u0964  <mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#f58722\" class=\"has-inline-color\">Navigation<\/mark> \u0915\u0947 \u092e\u0926\u0926 \u0938\u0947 \u0938\u092e\u091d\u0947  \u091c\u094b \u0928\u0947\u091a\u0947 \u0926\u093f\u090f \u0917\u092f\u0947\u0964 <\/li>\n<\/ol>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text has-media-on-the-right is-stacked-on-mobile\" style=\"grid-template-columns:auto 61%\"><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\">\n<ol>\n<li>\u0907\u0938 Section \u092e\u0947\u0902 \u0906\u092a\u0915\u094b \u0905\u092a\u0928\u0947  Product \u0915\u093e \u0928\u093e\u092e \u0921\u093e\u0932\u0928\u093e \u0939\u0948\u0964 <br> <br>Example \u0915\u0947 \u0932\u093f\u090f <strong>Product <mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#cd3636\" class=\"has-inline-color\">name*<\/mark>:<\/strong> &#8211; <strong><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#f58722\" class=\"has-inline-color\">Meggi<\/mark><\/strong> <\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<\/div><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"177\" src=\"https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-03-21-at-12.22.52_87e0bac7-1024x177.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-11954 size-full\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-03-21-at-12.22.52_87e0bac7-1024x177.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-03-21-at-12.22.52_87e0bac7-500x87.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-03-21-at-12.22.52_87e0bac7-768x133.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-03-21-at-12.22.52_87e0bac7.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text is-stacked-on-mobile\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"183\" src=\"https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-03-21-at-12.22.53_16504d80-1024x183.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-11955 size-full\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-03-21-at-12.22.53_16504d80-1024x183.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-03-21-at-12.22.53_16504d80-500x90.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-03-21-at-12.22.53_16504d80-768x137.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-03-21-at-12.22.53_16504d80.jpg 1067w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\">\n<p><strong>2.<\/strong> \u0905\u092a\u0928\u0947 \u0926\u094d\u0935\u093e\u0930\u093e \u0921\u093e\u0932\u0947 \u0917\u092f\u0947 Product \u0915\u094b \u0915\u093f\u0938 <mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#f58722\" class=\"has-inline-color\">Parent category<\/mark> \u092e\u0947\u0902 \u0906\u092a\u0915\u094b \u0926\u093f\u0916\u093e\u0928\u093e \u0939\u0948 \u092f\u093e \u0930\u0916\u0928\u093e \u0939\u0948\u0964 <br><br><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#cd3636\" class=\"has-inline-color\">Example<\/mark> \u0915\u0947 \u0932\u093f\u090f Meggi \u090f\u0915 Grocery Product \u0939\u0948\u0964<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text is-stacked-on-mobile\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"849\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-03-21-at-14.08.51_27bb8bd4-849x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-11961 size-full\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-03-21-at-14.08.51_27bb8bd4-849x1024.jpg 849w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-03-21-at-14.08.51_27bb8bd4-500x603.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-03-21-at-14.08.51_27bb8bd4-768x926.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-03-21-at-14.08.51_27bb8bd4.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 849px) 100vw, 849px\" \/><\/figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\">\n<p>\u0906\u092a\u0915\u094b <mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#f58722\" class=\"has-inline-color\">Select Parent Category<\/mark> \u0915\u0947 Option \u092e\u0947\u0902 \u091c\u093e \u0915\u0930 Grocery \u0915\u0947 \u0909\u092a\u094d\u092a\u0930 Click \u0915\u0930\u0928\u093e \u0939\u094b\u0917\u093e \u091c\u093f\u0938\u0938\u0947 \u0906\u092a\u0915\u093e Grocery Product Section \u092e\u0947\u0902 \u091a\u0932\u093e \u091c\u093e\u090f\u0917\u093e\u0964 <\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text has-media-on-the-right is-stacked-on-mobile\" style=\"grid-template-columns:auto 52%\"><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\">\n<p>3. <mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#cd3636\" class=\"has-inline-color\">Product brand<\/mark> \u092e\u0947\u0902 \u0906\u092a\u0915\u094b Meggi \u0915\u093e Company Name \u0921\u093e\u0932\u0928\u093e \u0939\u094b\u0917\u093e\u0964 \u091c\u0948\u0938\u0947 Meggi \u090f\u0915 <mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#f58722\" class=\"has-inline-color\">Nesly company<\/mark> \u092c\u0928\u093e\u0924\u0940 \u0939\u0948\u0964<br><br>Example \u0915\u0947 \u0932\u093f\u090f \u0907\u0938\u0915\u093e Brand Name \u092f\u093e Campany Name Nestl\u00e9 \u0939\u094b\u0917\u093e\u0964  <\/p>\n<\/div><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"169\" src=\"https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-03-21-at-12.22.53_973aefa7-1-1024x169.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-11956 size-full\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-03-21-at-12.22.53_973aefa7-1-1024x169.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-03-21-at-12.22.53_973aefa7-1-500x82.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-03-21-at-12.22.53_973aefa7-1-768x127.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-03-21-at-12.22.53_973aefa7-1.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text is-stacked-on-mobile\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"177\" src=\"https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240321-WA0022-1024x177.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-11962 size-full\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240321-WA0022-1024x177.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240321-WA0022-500x87.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240321-WA0022-768x133.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240321-WA0022.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\">\n<p>4. \u0915\u093f\u0938\u0940 Product \u0915\u093e <mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#cd3636\" class=\"has-inline-color\">Price 30<\/mark> \u0930\u0942\u092a\u0940 \u0939\u0948\u0964 \u092a\u0930 \u0906\u092a\u0915\u094b \u0909\u0938\u0915\u093e <mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#cd3636\" class=\"has-inline-color\">Price 30<\/mark> \u0915\u0947 \u091c\u0917\u0939 \u092a\u0930 Price Rate 50 \u0930\u0916\u0924\u0947 \u0939\u0948 \u0924\u094b\u0964<br><br>\u0906\u092a\u0915\u093e Price Rate <mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#f58722\" class=\"has-inline-color\">50 Fake<\/mark> Price \u0939\u094b\u0917\u093e\u0964<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text has-media-on-the-right is-stacked-on-mobile\"><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\">\n<p>5. \u091c\u093f\u0938 Price \u0915\u0947 \u0938\u093e\u0925 \u0906\u092a \u0905\u092a\u0928\u093e Product \u0915\u094b Sale \u0915\u0930\u0928\u093e \u091a\u093e\u0939\u0924\u0947 \u0939\u0948\u0964 \u0909\u0938\u0915\u093e Price \u0906\u092a Selling Price \u092e\u0947\u0902 \u0921\u093e\u0932 \u0938\u0915\u0924\u0947 \u0939\u0948\u0964<br><br>Example \u0915\u0947 \u0932\u093f\u090f <mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#cd3636\" class=\"has-inline-color\">30 Rupee<\/mark> \u0906\u092a\u0915\u093e Selling Price \u0939\u094b\u0917\u093e\u0964 <\/p>\n<\/div><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"162\" src=\"https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240321-WA0023-1024x162.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-11963 size-full\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240321-WA0023-1024x162.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240321-WA0023-500x79.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240321-WA0023-768x122.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240321-WA0023.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text is-stacked-on-mobile\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"165\" src=\"https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240321-WA0024-1024x165.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-11965 size-full\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240321-WA0024-1024x165.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240321-WA0024-500x81.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240321-WA0024-768x124.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240321-WA0024.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\">\n<p>6. Buying Price \u0906\u092a\u0915\u094b \u092f\u0939 \u092c\u0924\u093e\u0924\u093e \u0939\u0948 \u0915\u093f \u0905\u092a\u0928\u0947 \u0905\u092a\u0928\u0947 Product \u0915\u094b \u0915\u093f\u0938 Rate \u092e\u0947 \u0932\u093f\u092f\u093e \u0917\u092f\u093e \u0939\u0948\u0964<br><br><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#cd3636\" class=\"has-inline-color\">Example<\/mark> \u0915\u0947 \u0932\u093f\u090f 20 Rupee \u0906\u092a\u0915\u093e Whole-seller Rate \u0939\u0948\u0964 \u091c\u094b \u0906\u092a\u0915\u094b \u092e\u093f\u0932\u093e \u0939\u0948\u0964 <\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text has-media-on-the-right is-stacked-on-mobile\"><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\">\n<p>7. Initial Quantity \u0906\u092a\u0915\u094b \u092f\u0947 \u092c\u0924\u093e\u0924\u093e \u0939\u0948 \u0915\u093f \u0906\u092a\u0915\u0947 \u092a\u093e\u0938 \u0915\u093f\u0924\u0928\u0947 Menu \u092c\u091a\u0947 \u0939\u0948\u0964 <br><br>Example \u0915\u0947 \u0932\u093f\u090f \u0905\u0917\u0930 \u0906\u092a\u0915\u0947 \u092a\u093e\u0938 <mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#f58722\" class=\"has-inline-color\">100 Menu<\/mark> \u0939\u0948 \u0924\u094b\u0964 \u0906\u092a \u092f\u0939\u093e \u0921\u093e\u0932 \u0915\u0947 \u0909\u0938\u0947 <mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#f58722\" class=\"has-inline-color\">Show <\/mark>\u0915\u0930\u0935\u093e \u0938\u0915\u0924\u0947 \u0939\u0948\u0964 <\/p>\n<\/div><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"184\" src=\"https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240321-WA0025-1024x184.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-11964 size-full\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240321-WA0025-1024x184.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240321-WA0025-500x90.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240321-WA0025-768x138.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240321-WA0025.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text is-stacked-on-mobile\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"178\" src=\"https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240321-WA0026-1024x178.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-11969 size-full\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240321-WA0026-1024x178.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240321-WA0026-500x87.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240321-WA0026-768x134.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240321-WA0026.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\">\n<p>8. <mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#cd3636\" class=\"has-inline-color\">SKU Bar Code<\/mark> \u090f\u0915 \u0938\u093e\u0925 \u0906\u092a\u0915\u0947 \u092c\u0939\u0941\u0924 \u0938\u0947 \u0915\u093e\u092e \u0915\u0930 \u0938\u0915\u0924\u0947 \u0939\u0948\u0964 \u091c\u0948\u0938\u0947 \u0915\u093f \u0906\u092a SKU \u0915\u094b Scan \u0915\u0930 \u0915\u0947 \u0905\u092a\u0928\u093e Stock \u092c\u0928\u093e \u0915\u0930 \u0930\u0916 \u0938\u0915\u0924\u0947 \u0939\u0948\u0964 <br><br>Sale Count \u0915\u0930 \u0915\u0947 \u0909\u0938\u0915\u093e details \u0930\u0916 \u0938\u0915\u0924\u093e \u0939\u0948\u0964 \u092f\u0947 \u0906\u092a\u0915\u094b \u092f\u0939 \u092d\u0940 \u091c\u093e\u0928\u0915\u093e\u0930\u0940 \u0926\u0947\u0924\u093e \u0930\u0939\u0947\u0917\u093e \u0915\u093f \u0906\u092a\u0915\u0947 \u092a\u093e\u0938 \u0915\u093f\u0924\u0928\u093e Stock \u092c\u091a\u093e \u0939\u0941\u0906 \u0939\u0948\u0964 <br><\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text is-stacked-on-mobile\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"262\" src=\"https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/Screenshot_20240321-152849-1-1-3-1024x262.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-11984 size-full\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/Screenshot_20240321-152849-1-1-3-1024x262.png 1024w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/Screenshot_20240321-152849-1-1-3-500x128.png 500w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/Screenshot_20240321-